parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy properly or at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A rusty subframe can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting and corrosion of the subframe can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential fatalities.
symptoms: Strange noises
